snippet.textDisplay:
Anthony and his team are great!

These videos are entertaining and very educational. People tend to judge others based off of stereotypes, etc. and so hearing these conversations with people in certain communities allows you to get past those prejudices. So thank you for opening people's minds and helping them build up empathy for people they don't understand.

Also I really appreciate how friendly and respectful he is during interviews, everyone seems at ease and he doesn't put people down. Anthony makes an effort to understand them and that's great!

We don't know much about the people behind the scenes, but the videos are always well filmed and high quality and the editing is well done (I especially like all the hidden jokes).

So thank you to everyone behind making these videos! I'm sure you don't get enough appreciation. Thank you for opening up people's mind, teaching them empathy for those different from them, and for making great content!
